('93972','32354','5','Modern villa in a quiet residential area in Costa de la Calma'),
('93973','32355','5','Costa de la Calma is located in the municipality of Calvia in the southwest of Mallorca and is one of the most popular residential areas in this region. This villa was built in 2010 on a 1.7000m² big plot surrounded by a green zone.  The modern styled villa offers approximately 230m² of living space. These are spread over 2 floors. Over the entrance on the top floor (Street Level) you enter a bright living-dining room with modern open kitchen which adjoins a laundry room. Here are still a guest bathroom,  the master bedroom with en suite bathroom and a terrace overlooking the garden and the pool.\r\nIn the basement (garden level) has a 40m² large multi-room, 1 guest bedroom with en suite bathroom, an office, laundry room and a bathroom.\r\nNestled in the landscaped garden (artificial grass) is a 15mx3,5m large pool.\r\nThe equipment of the villa with air conditioning (cold) include an electric floor heating, double glazed picture windows and laminate flooring. The modern and well maintained villa offers even 1 storage room, 1 open- and 2 covered parking spaces.\r\n'),
